text: Andorra–San Marino relations are foreign relations between Andorra and San Marino. Diplomatic relations between them were established on November 30, 1995. Both nations are members of the Council of Europe. == See also == * Foreign relations of Andorra * Foreign relations of San Marino * Andorra–European Union relations * San Marino–European Union relations ==References== Category:Bilateral relations of Andorra Andorra
